{"tid":1581703,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"訓唔著嘅你 入嚟開解下小弟","createTime":"2019-09-19T16:26:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T05:53:00.000Z","uid":302578,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"539c70295808ee9efedd5b016d3108a6b5d993d8","tid":1581703,"uid":302578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T16:26:19.000Z","msg":"就咁<br />\n近排因為d事(自己衰)同最close嗰班反反地面 搞到自己好唔開心<br />\n見到佢哋成班約咗出嚟 但係冇搵自己 我個心就銀住銀住<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇咗佢哋好似已經冇晒依靠<br />\n之前幾年有咩都係搵佢哋講 而家得返自己一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搵fd食個飯又冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搵人一齊出去發夢又冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想搵班人飲酒講心事又冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要怪就怪自己啦 可能我性格真係有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n已經自己發夢左兩個月有多喇 有冇人訓唔著陪我鳩fing<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"274e770418d1bcd8c3c8e363a48fcdbb9976261f","tid":1581703,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T16:26:46.000Z","msg":"【行動post/多圖】922和你suck 8大行動（更新版）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1581619\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1581619</a><br />\n<br />\n【行動文宣】請廣傳<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">922 suck 4.0 各有各玩</span></span><br />\n1）影帝不死隊，入機場cover突擊隊<br />\n2）先塞青衣，再視乎情況轉戰商場<br />\n3）直接和理suck商場<br />\n4）全港交通測試，工程RB隊<br />\n5）加入單車隊-會有單車小將帶領<br />\n6）黨鐵突擊小隊！（機場突擊隊已有一定人數後）<br />\n7）東涌郊野一日遊，玩無線電walkie，玩無人機<br />\n8) 我係機場人-食錯藍絲野食物中毒 準備 SL 被罷工<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">兄弟爬山，各有各做</span><br />\n<del>我地另外有秘密小隊行動</del><br />\n<br />\nTG : <a href=\"https://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=kSOQn%2BAsZtDywzIR1u7IPwogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=f1a1a26e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"ea0e878c6a9bbadb228cdfba7e6dbcfa89df5bd6","tid":1581703,"uid":302578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T16:27:15.000Z","msg":"連登有愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76acd78920803566c6b6114ac40a1a4340684ea0","tid":1581703,"uid":204265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T16:28:27.000Z","msg":"I know that feel bro"},{"pid":"4466facb9914bb160203e2c91d1c28740d98da81","tid":1581703,"uid":302578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T16:28:40.000Z","msg":"乳搖巴多謝你覆我<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a23f03579028675c5f9dee86c0e5a14c9d8e777d","tid":1581703,"uid":302578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76acd78920803566c6b6114ac40a1a4340684ea0","tid":1581703,"uid":204265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T16:28:27.000Z","msg":"I know that feel bro"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T16:28:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"534725985a9368df23b1a47c8ec945ffa1e01160","tid":1581703,"uid":57308,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T16:29:07.000Z","msg":"知自己性格有問題又唔改<br />\n算9數啦"},{"pid":"1528c47e3ba35cd3987e3ff0e41e7e0674fac453","tid":1581703,"uid":302578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"534725985a9368df23b1a47c8ec945ffa1e01160","tid":1581703,"uid":57308,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T16:29:07.000Z","msg":"知自己性格有問題又唔改<br />\n算9數啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T16:31:29.000Z","msg":"我係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2d406782783e1fa0a2f7a689789364356aea2e2","tid":1581703,"uid":302578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"